column16: Kevin Kiermaier flies out to center fielder Rusney Castillo.
Ben Zobrist doubles (34) on a fly ball to center fielder Rusney Castillo.   Brandon Guyer scores.
Sean Rodriguez called out on strikes.
Dioner Navarro pops out to first baseman Mike Napoli in foul territory.
Edwin Encarnacion flies out to right fielder Allen Craig.
Steve Tolleson grounds out, shortstop Brock Holt to first baseman Mike Napoli.
